*Svira* se na čembalu. (It is played on the harpsichord.)

Gitara *svira* zvuke. (The guitar plays sounds.)

Ona *svira* saksofon. (She plays the saxophone.)

Svirači su igrali do jutra. (The musicians played until morning.)

Njegov brat *svira* bas. (His brother plays the bass.)

*Svirali* su muziku u parku. (They played music in the park.)

Ona *svira* klarinet. (She plays the clarinet.)

Oni su *svirali* dugo. (They played for a long time.)